{% block content %}

  <section class="post-header">
    <div class="post-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; Back to Home</a>
      <span class="blog-category">Results</span>
      <h1>Client Success Stories</h1>
      <p style="color:#ccc;margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:1.05rem;">Real results from real businesses. Every case study below is a documented engagement with measurable outcomes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="post-body" style="max-width:900px;margin:3rem auto;padding:0 1.5rem;">

    <div class="cards" style="margin-top:1rem;">

      <article class="card" style="text-align:left;">
        <span class="blog-category">Custom Wood Carving / E-commerce</span>
        <h3>Joe Tiki Custom Wood Carving</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Running a custom wood carving hobby out of a garage with almost no marketing. Joe had a website he managed himself and minimal social media presence, but no real strategy driving customers to his business.</p>
        <p><strong>What we did:</strong> Built a focused social media content strategy and grew his presence from nearly nothing. Created behind-the-scenes videos of the carving process, before-and-after transformation content, and customer story posts — then scheduled them consistently across Facebook and Instagram. Also provided hands-on business consulting including scheduling systems, business structure guidance, and connecting him with trusted resources.</p>
        <p><strong>Results:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;color:#ccc;">
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">650,000+ views</span> across two 28-day periods</li>
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">10x business growth</span> in one year</li>
          <li>Upgraded from garage hobby to full wood shop operation</li>
          <li>Revenue tripled from social media-driven demand</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;">Services: Social media management, content creation, business consulting</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="text-align:left;">
        <span class="blog-category">Events / Community</span>
        <h3>Palm Coast Farmers Market</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> A local farmers market needing to increase weekend foot traffic and vendor participation in a competitive community events space.</p>
        <p><strong>What we did:</strong> Developed a focused Facebook and Instagram content strategy built around vendor spotlights, fresh produce visuals, community event promotion, and consistent weekly posting leading up to each market day.</p>
        <p><strong>Results:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;color:#ccc;">
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">687,000+ views</span> in just 30 days</li>
          <li>Weekend foot traffic surged — vendors felt the difference immediately</li>
          <li>Became a go-to community event through consistent social presence</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;">Services: Social media management, content creation</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="text-align:left;">
        <span class="blog-category">Restaurant</span>
        <h3>Tokyo Japanese Steakhouse</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Needed more bookings and foot traffic in a competitive restaurant market with limited marketing budget.</p>
        <p><strong>What we did:</strong> Created a video-first content campaign showcasing the hibachi cooking experience, chef skills, and customer reactions. Published short-form video content designed to capture local attention and drive immediate action.</p>
        <p><strong>Results:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;color:#ccc;">
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">Same-day bookings</span> from the first video campaign</li>
          <li>Immediate increase in foot traffic from social media discovery</li>
          <li>Strong local brand awareness from viral-style content</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;">Services: Video content production, social media</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="text-align:left;">
        <span class="blog-category">Automotive</span>
        <h3>A&amp;D Auto Workz</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> An auto shop looking to grow revenue through better visibility and consistent customer acquisition.</p>
        <p><strong>What we did:</strong> Implemented a content strategy using all four high-performing content types: behind-the-scenes shop footage, before-and-after vehicle transformations, local community engagement, and real customer testimonials.</p>
        <p><strong>Results:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;color:#ccc;">
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">~3x revenue growth</span> in approximately two months</li>
          <li>Authentic, locally-focused content drove consistent new customer acquisition</li>
          <li>Strong word-of-mouth amplified by social proof content</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;">Services: Social media management, content creation</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="text-align:left;">
        <span class="blog-category">Finance / Media</span>
        <h3>Crowded Market Report (CMR Publishing)</h3>
        <p><strong>Challenge:</strong> A $5,000/month financial media publishing company needed professional social media management, YouTube content editing and uploads, and a complete website overhaul to match the quality of their brand.</p>
        <p><strong>What we did:</strong> Rebuilt their website from scratch for clarity and professionalism. Made their branding consistent across all social media platforms — updated headshots, visuals, and messaging. Focused on YouTube Shorts where they severely lacked presence, introducing AI-powered tools and software to maximize efficiency. Also went above and beyond scope — secured sponsor meetings, set up interviews, and traveled last minute to help build their recording studio from scratch.</p>
        <p><strong>Results:</strong></p>
        <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem;color:#ccc;">
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">YouTube views increased</span> through strategic Shorts focus</li>
          <li>Complete website overhaul — professional, organized, clear messaging</li>
          <li>Consistent branding across all social media platforms</li>
          <li>Secured sponsor meetings and built recording studio on-site</li>
          <li><span class="stat-highlight">5-star Google review</span> and ongoing referral relationship</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#888;">Services: Social media management, YouTube content, website rebuild, AI integration, business consulting</p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="post-callout" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      <p>Every client engagement starts with a conversation. There's no cookie-cutter approach — we build the strategy around your business.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="post-cta-box">
      <h3>Want to Be Our Next Success Story?</h3>
      <p>Get a free SEO audit or book a strategy call — and let's build something that actually moves the needle for your business.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;">
        <a href="/seo-audit/" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get a Free SEO Audit &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large" style="background:transparent;border:2px solid var(--blue);color:var(--blue);">Book a Strategy Call &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

{% endblock %}
